                        <interp inst="t18460511-name-818" type="given" value="CATHARINE"></interp>CATHARINE HALEY</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> My husband was out all that evening—he never came home till I went and fetched him, after losing my things—the prisoner came to me on the 21st of April, and left on the 30th.</p>
